data.description: Welcome to the highly sought after and coveted community of Wolf Ranch! Built in 2020 by Perry Homes, this stunning Northwest facing 1 story features 4 bedrooms, 3 full bathrooms, office, and bonus room. Upon entry, you are immediately welcomed with detailed tray ceilings in the open foyer. To your left discover 2 secondary bedrooms with ample natural light and plenty of closet space. A full guest bathroom is convenient to both bedrooms. Continue your journey and to the right you will find a generous sized bonus room that can be a used as a media room, play room, or an additional living area- imagine the possibilities! Up ahead, is the dedicated office beautifully framed with French Doors. The open concept kitchen is a chefs delight complete with stainless steel appliances, including gas range, granite countertops, large kitchen island, and plenty of cabinet space. Large windows throughout this home flood the space with natural light, creating an inviting and warm ambiance. A third bedroom offers an en suite bath perfect for those who desire privacy and convenience. Retreat to the spacious owners suite. Relax in your soaking tub or wash the day off in your separate shower. With an expansive closet, dual vanities and sinks, your morning routine just got easier! Enjoy outdoor living with the covered patio facing a tranquil greenspace and no neighbors behind the home. The extended patio is perfect for both relaxation and large gatherings for entertaining guests. Elegant LVP flooring located in all main living areas. Garage features epoxy floors and plumbed for water softener. Special connection for generator hook up has been installed outside this home. Located in close proximity to Wolf Ranch Elementary, and the newer amenity center River Camp which includes a large fitness center, sparking pool and splash pad, outdoor grills and pavilion, and playground.   Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your forever home- schedule your appointment to view today!
